                +b information."
            implementation "Organizations should implement logging mechanisms that capture the specified
                +b data fields and ensure these logs are protected, retained, and accessible for
                +b audit purposes."
        { related_standards
            { "ISO/IEC 27001"
                section "A.12.4"
                description "Logging and monitoring - emphasizes the importance of event logging and
