        requirement_id "IEC 62443-4-2: CR 2.9(b)"
        title "Audit Storage Capacity - Exceeded"
        description "This requirement focuses on ensuring that systems have the capability to detect
            +b and respond to situations where the storage capacity for audit logs is
            +b exceeded. The objective is to maintain the integrity and availability of audit
            +b logs, which are crucial for security monitoring and forensic analysis."
