                    +b prevent storage overflow while ensuring logs are preserved for the required
                    +b retention period."
            {
                aspect_id "3"
                aspect_title "Capacity Planning"
                aspect_description "Conduct regular capacity planning exercises to predict future storage needs
                    +b based on system usage and audit log generation rates. This helps in ensuring
                    +b that adequate storage resources are available to handle audit data without
                    +b interruption."
        [ related_standards
            {
                standard_name "NIST SP 800-92"
                reference_title "Guide to Computer Security Log Management"
                reference_description "This document provides guidelines for effectively managing computer security
