                    +b the need to manage storage capacity effectively."
            {
                standard_name "CIS Controls v8"
                reference_title "Control 8: Audit Log Management"
                reference_description "This control outlines key practices for managing audit logs, including the need
                    +b for monitoring log storage capacity and ensuring that logs are retained
                    +b according to policy."
    {
        id "FSA-CR 2.9 RE(1)"
        check_description "Components shall provide the capability to issue a warning when the allocated
