            {
                standard "ISO/IEC 27002:2013"
                reference "12.4.1 Event Logging"
                description "Advises on the implementation of event logging, including the necessity of
                    +b ensuring logs are stored securely and remain available for review, aligning
                    +b with the need to monitor storage capacity."